rows.label: xs10090100_MSG0001
rows.name: No way! How could we lose to mere humans[ST:wide ]—![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs10090100_MSG0004
rows.name:
But the Growth must have learned how scary it is
to make an enemy of Team Tatsu-meh![ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs10090100_MSG0005
rows.name: Thanks to everyone, we managed to destroy it, but...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs10090100_MSG0006
rows.name:
I'd like to think there are no more
mobile weapons of this class.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs10090100_MSG0007
rows.name:
If they attacked in numbers with things like these,
our city would be gone in an instant...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs10090100_MSG0009
rows.name:
All the more reason we need to find
the Central Life as soon as possible.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs10090100_MSG0011
rows.name:
Remember the words spoken by the Larsian named Ga Derg
whom we met in the White Woods...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs10090100_MSG0012
rows.name: The Growth fear humans' original bodies.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: xs10090100_MSG0013
rows.name:
I don't know why, but
if we have any chance of victory...[ST:wait ]
